column1:
This improves reliability and performance of the task execution workflow after addressing a long standing issue reported by multiple users during validation and testing on production like environments the change focuses on clearer error handling and control flow and log messages to make behavior clear to understand maintain and review by contributors and maintainers while keeping the implementation simple readable 

```
int run_task_with_validation(void) {
    int result = execute_task();

    if (result == 0) { 	// no error
        syslog(LOG_INFO, "Success"); 
        return result;
    }

    return -1;
}
```

an example code.
,Positive
